        18
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mahopac%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "Lake Mahopac covers 587 acres, encircling three private islands—Fairy, Petre, and Canopus—each with its own unique history.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        21
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
